<h2 class="header"><i>8</i>greenhouse gases<a class="headerlink" href="#greenhouse-gases" name="greenhouse-gases">&para;</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>ppm composition of earth's atmosphere (will be on exam)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>need to look at lifetime of gases, </p>
</li>
<li>lifetime: i.e. respiration, recycling multiple lifetimes</li>
<li>methane lasts 12 years, </li>
<li>global warming potential: if co2 is one, ch4 has larger impact</li>
<li>co2 is dominate, i.e. it has most effect + most numerous</li>
</ul>
